Name: Average resolution time following 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average duration from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Accepted + In Progress'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average delay caused by 'Accepted + Wait - User' in the 'Completed + In Call' activity
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of 'Accepted + Wait - User' in cases leading to 'Completed + Closed'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Longest time from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to any subsequent activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001E27CECF0A0> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest time from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Accepted + Assigned'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + Assigned'

Name: Time difference between 'Accepted + Wait - User' and 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation' in completing the process
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Average time reduction in 'Completed + In Call' when preceded by 'Accepted + Wait - User'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total time spent in 'Accepted + Wait - User' for cases with 'Completed + Cancelled'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Cancelled'

Name: Median duration from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Time variance of 'Accepted + Wait - User' across different countries
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case grouped by the last value of resource country

Name: Distribution of time for 'Accepted + Wait - User' across different org:groups
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case grouped by the last value of org:group

Name: Average time from 'Accepted + Wait - User' to 'Completed + In Call' across different variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Impact of 'Accepted + Wait - User' on the total resolution time of incidents
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'
